{"tid":1399750,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"721貨van司機, 現身維園「撐警集會」上台發言","createTime":"2019-08-03T09:30:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T18:05:10.000Z","uid":134071,"like":2,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9cf7f3e20b36fae29ba8f1732e62a60a2a70e2a7","tid":1399750,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T09:30:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190803/59892759\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190803%2F59892759&d=MMgAXMBwwZFGDPTkcL6JsZ1QB7Ma9ovE6nvZW%2BRTqP4%3D&h=cf89baf7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190803%2F59892759&h=52e45217\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190803/59892759</a><br />\n<br />\n 2019年08月03日<br />\n【撐警集會】何君堯突現身發言兼領唱 台下歡呼：支持你！做特首！ <br />\n.....<br />\n何君堯約下午4時突然現身，全場即歡呼。何指，香港真係要加油，並非如黑衣人般傷害香港，「做好自己就係幫香港，只要黑衣人唔好搞亂香港，已經好大幫忙」。何指，兩個月吵吵鬧鬧因為逃犯條例，香港96年已有相關法例，但大陸及澳門不能引渡，是有人別有用心，又形容「讀得最多書嘅大學生變咗文盲」。他在台上領唱《男兒當自強》、《獅子山下》，台下一度有支持者高叫「做特首呀！」，其他人則大叫「支持你！何君堯！」，主持鄧德成更高叫多謝何君堯「帶領呢場運動」，現場儼如何君堯造勢大會。<br />\n.....<br />\n<strong>大會壓軸嘉賓，是於7月21日晚，曾駕駛客貨車於干諾道中企圖衝破示威者路障，結果與示威者發生口角及爭執的客貨車司機陳先生。</strong>他上台呼籲大家停止爭拗，「大家嘈交係嘈唔贏，大家都後生過，網上爭輸贏，令人忘記何謂尊重，何謂禮貌」。他指，30年前香港年輕人面對面對吸毒問題，現時面對網絡問題，將來也許會有新問題，「唔好鬧佢哋，但係咪要教好佢哋呢？」"},{"pid":"04ba66f4ac94c9f83629542b1b8b12f2ccc5c761","tid":1399750,"uid":134071,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T09:31:20.000Z","msg":"而家諗番, 貨van司機可能係專登引示威者出手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E/article/20190722/s00001/1563736946823\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E8%25A6%2581%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190722%2Fs00001%2F1563736946823&d=MMgAXMBwwZFGDPTkcL6JsZ1QB7Ma9ovE6nvZW%2BRTqP4%3D&h=fb8b1741\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E8%25A6%2581%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190722%2Fs00001%2F1563736946823&h=d100901f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E/article/20190722/s00001/1563736946823</a><br />\n<br />\n2019年7月22日星期一<br />\n客貨車圖衝示威者路障起推撞 司機捱打<br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】一批示威者昨日佔領中環附近的一段馬路，當中一輛客貨車在干諾道中往上環方向的路段，遭示威者擺下的路障阻礙，客貨車一度企圖衝破路障遭示威者阻止，客貨車司機其後落車，與示威者爭執及口角，其間有示威者希望重新擺設路障時，司機上前推撞示威者，觸發雙方衝突，司機被圍毆，現場義工及急救員其後分隔雙方，客貨車司機被打傷由救護員送院治理。打鬥期間，客貨車被人破壞，擋風玻璃及多塊玻璃破裂。<br />\n<br />\n（反修例風暴）"},{"pid":"052eae411d0dfb418028a974fb4e30eefb971c54","tid":1399750,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T09:31:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09565086d0694b5a04a9aafd2f8c75237138ed35","tid":1399750,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T09:33:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b25c72721773334ce4c4370103ae943f63fd4cc0","tid":1399750,"uid":83002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T09:33:17.000Z","msg":"最尾果句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26890af210f898452355262f6e03d48fa968fffb","tid":1399750,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T09:35:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3e0b3d456ac3c5fa4468040379300252c6776ad","tid":1399750,"uid":228143,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T09:37:00.000Z","msg":"更加證明係鄉黑派來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae8ba23b127e25cb2e57e2a61aa48666d38c24ae","tid":1399750,"uid":140924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T09:38:17.000Z","msg":"Sorry 我重點去咗呢度<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>他在台上領唱《男兒當自強》、《獅子山下》，台下一度有支持者高叫「做特首呀！」，其他人則大叫「支持你！何君堯！」</blockquote><br />\n何律師真係歌影視三棲。"},{"pid":"30e58e02511e8214dbe41a3c4f411c299e995d6c","tid":1399750,"uid":134071,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d3e0b3d456ac3c5fa4468040379300252c6776ad","tid":1399750,"uid":228143,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T09:37:00.000Z","msg":"更加證明係鄉黑派來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T09:38:18.000Z","msg":"引示威者出手, 之後再俾紅媒做fake news抹黑示威者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48d6c5e13d38caa2e7c0ccb9969928e87c44810b","tid":1399750,"uid":237517,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T09:39:26.000Z","msg":"姓何條友仲可以光明正大搞撐警<br />\n<br />\n香港真係痴撚線"},{"pid":"112f9811149db528a3681831b8e2d3a978079d6f","tid":1399750,"uid":202137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T09:39:34.000Z","msg":"今次唔用籐條水喉通用咩教？"},{"pid":"8407995947898adb9a446ac7f14b93023099bafb","tid":1399750,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T09:42:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a280e042c8a6df168d0cc5ebb7bd4e9f1969621","tid":1399750,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T10:09:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e2ed772a72b80a8ffcaf5054938374de94a598e","tid":1399750,"uid":284590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"112f9811149db528a3681831b8e2d3a978079d6f","tid":1399750,"uid":202137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T09:39:34.000Z","msg":"今次唔用籐條水喉通用咩教？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T18:05:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}